{"tid":1758460,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大快活(00052.HK) 2019中期業績","createTime":"2019-11-27T05:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T11:00:13.000Z","uid":44517,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"46976f313d20302043e6c89784e9f1b5c82ea916","tid":1758460,"uid":44517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"大快活(<a href=\"http://00052.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00052.HK&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=4c110d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00052.HK</a>)  公布9月底止中期業績，純利按年大幅倒退43.1%至5,726.2萬元，每股盈利44.28仙。公司表示，純利倒退主要原因為採用新會計準則帶來之賬面影響、租金及工資成本持續上升，及市場氣氛偏弱。撇除採納《香港財務報告準則》中「租賃」部份之1,380萬元之負面影響，純利實按年僅倒退29.4%至7,110萬元。<br />\n<br />\n公司宣派每股中期股息23仙，少於去年同期之37仙，派息比率52%，高於去年同期之47%。<br />\n<br />\n期內收入按年增長4.5%至15.39億元，毛利率按年下降2.4個百分點至11.3%。至9月底止，公司於本港經營155間店鋪，包括143間快餐店及12間特色餐廳；於中國經營12間店鋪。期內於本港新開7間分店，於中國新增1間分店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.978834/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.978834%2F2&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=44c65c13\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.978834/2</a><br />\n<br />\n又話大快活係黃，點解純利仲可以少三成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beae75d880b0fc0b86e1dad4178541a00fa727a6","tid":1758460,"uid":26224,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"租金，人工，食材都升又加唔到價"},{"pid":"c3392c83586cf8ea5fcee7c8760adf5c549c373e","tid":1758460,"uid":283700,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"有錢賺算係咁，捱多排藍店死哂就稱霸。  出黎做生意呢d位要捱。"},{"pid":"e3213a19d4514a5a1dcec0cf83b827ba847b70ea","tid":1758460,"uid":12705,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"大快活都咁<br />\n諗下富臨美心"},{"pid":"3f9f1b8ef7810f5eec2632c6344d73b355d43